  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of rapeseed oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat. Add the onion and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the mushroom, carrot, and green pepper. Cook until the vegetables are tender, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the fry-grind-rice-khao-khua, soy sauce, salt, and black pepper. Stir-fry for 2-3 minutes, until the rice is heated through.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a serving platter and garnish with chopped fresh parsley.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
